<A>__{late, late at night. the plant is silent. the property seems empty, until we notice pete irving standing alone inside the gates, staring up at the station. after a beat, he picks up a rock and hurls it at the plant. it misses. not that it would do anything if it hit. he reaches for another, throws it. then another, and another. he hurls rock after rock at the gigantic plant. then, overwhelmed by his impotence, he lets out a terrifying yell.}
